{"tid":2193810,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"百萬YouTuber「熱吻同床睡19歲親妹」賺點閱！　妹崩潰…網傻眼轟爆","createTime":"2020-09-08T06:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T01:35:58.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c65572a292f48ad84014fc72e6bd697329d1a2dc","tid":2193810,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:12:33.000Z","msg":"日本YouTuber「桐崎栄二.きりざきえいじ」頻道擁有292萬訂閱數，他於今年4月上傳的一支影片在近日引發關注，影片內容為他和妹妹2人輪流轉動轉盤，並完成指定項目動作，而選項中竟然有「親親」這個選項，兄妹倆毫不避諱地在鏡頭前完成任務，許多網友質疑「到底看了什麼」？<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒報導，4月時「桐崎栄二.きりざきえいじ」上傳了一部名為「24小時與妹妹用輪盤決定生活，家庭崩潰開始&hellip;」的影片，大致上的內容為自己和妹妹輪流使用轉盤，轉出接下來要做的事，但妹妹一開始就轉到「接吻」的勁爆選項，2人也僅隔著保鮮膜就「親下去」。<br />\n<br />\n短短幾秒的畫面衝擊了觀眾的心理，事後妹妹崩潰地打了哥哥一巴掌，整個人滾到床上耍賴。事實上，不只有這影片，在他其它的影片當中，兄妹2人也時常做出親吻行為，還有同床共眠的親密畫面。<br />\n<br />\n網友在看完影片後紛紛留言回應，「以家人的關係來說，這樣的舉動好像有點過火了&hellip;」、「這種想都想不到的事情，他們竟然做了&hellip;」、「怎麼有辦法辦到這樣的事！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=15&amp;v=LK5GFiFOBT8&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D15%26v%3DLK5GFiFOBT8%26feature%3Demb_title&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=878bcac9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=15&amp;v=LK5GFiFOBT8&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"2b5913c5cca61cd1583801fb589165628035562f","tid":2193810,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5125/d5125277.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5125%2Fd5125277.jpg&h=fb5a6c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本YouTuber「桐崎栄二.きりざきえいじ」4月上傳一支名為「24小時與妹妹用輪盤決定生活，家庭崩潰開始&hellip;」的影片。（圖／翻攝自YouTube「桐崎栄二.きりざきえいじ」）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5125/d5125278.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5125%2Fd5125278.jpg&h=227a7e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兄妹倆只隔著保鮮膜接吻。（圖／翻攝自YouTube「桐崎栄二.きりざきえいじ」）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5125/d5125279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5125%2Fd5125279.jpg&h=eed07eb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n妹妹崩潰到在床上翻滾耍賴。（圖／翻攝自YouTube「桐崎栄二.きりざきえいじ」）"},{"pid":"2c12193441709641abc982b2a00a5fc655b5e476","tid":2193810,"uid":143093,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:14:34.000Z","msg":"但我覺得好有氣質同埋好天然"},{"pid":"d17e1980ab29b5a27337b1727d95db91d260c1c2","tid":2193810,"uid":135867,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034ece594b7b7a2f7d8f544f3fc97b86693c8548","tid":2193810,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:14:37.000Z","msg":"亂倫ready<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951501653dc48c83d1db59dd6fb14ecb9cca18d3","tid":2193810,"uid":135867,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d17e1980ab29b5a27337b1727d95db91d260c1c2","tid":2193810,"uid":135867,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2495a901236bb1f6857eef83cb71c856e47b915f","tid":2193810,"uid":243380,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:16:35.000Z","msg":"能幹的妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc2fa9c65432efa2067783a645e84c898290c68","tid":2193810,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"咁似之前鬼佬咀自己姐姐同老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d19ffc8751b80a5241de0a383c5dd464e4d5e87","tid":2193810,"uid":59